{"tid":119470,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人嘅兄弟姊妹係廢青/毒撚？","createTime":"2017-02-13T18:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T05:51:26.000Z","uid":25225,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa6d02f365b5856ebf79b5eda94844d1171d131","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"我21歲仲讀緊書，哥哥就大我兩年，而家跟爸爸返工<br />\n<br />\n話說細個我同哥哥都仲會一齊玩，但越大越生疏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使大家都係屋企都係各自玩電腦女<br />\n<br />\n我地中學開始讀唔同學校，雖然無特別留意，但都知佢真係無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我明我明你地一定會覺得我大驚小怪，哥哥只不過係個一街都係嘅毒撚。<br />\n<br />\n就因為咁，我先想問下大家呢種毒撚係咪正常：<br />\n<br />\n1. 除左打機/睇書，乜都唔上心<br />\n<br />\n爸爸係公司叫哥哥幫手係紙皮箱上面黐紙；爸先示範點黐(封箱膠紙黐住a4白紙四邊)，再由哥哥自己做。點知佢淨係用張膠紙打直貼住其中一條邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同無黐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 貼身嘅事都完全唔肯處理<br />\n佢近兩三個月都無剪過頭髮，媽媽新年前係咁叫佢剪，幾個鐘叫一次叫到發脾氣都叫唔郁... (樓下$50理髮路程3分鐘)<br />\n<br />\n又有次哥哥最常著嘅鞋爛爛地，鞋底就黎甩。媽媽叫佢買過對鞋，佢竟然過等對鞋完全爛左先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 覺得人生無意義<br />\n係畢業之後哥哥有好長一段時間無野做，日日係屋企打機。<br />\n媽媽成日叫佢搵d野做下，返份hea工/ 搵個興趣/ 打下工咩都好... 當然都係叫唔郁<br />\n有次媽媽崩潰咁問佢<br />\n媽：到底你係有咩想做？搵份工好無？<br />\n哥：嗰d野做黎無意義<br />\n媽：咁做咩對你黎講係有意義？<br />\n哥：無，人生都都無意義<br />\n媽：意義唔係你等就會係個到跌落黎，係要你自己搵返黎<br />\n哥：⋯<br />\n<br />\n然後爸爸用關係幫哥哥R到份工返黎，點知佢竟然話：你唔好幫我做決定<br />\n<br />\n頂真係俾佢吹到啤一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c414fe819ef6f0940d53b034517bab9d8c4af15","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:30:42.000Z","msg":"未打完就post左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就打到呢到 有相似經驗嘅巴絲可以分享下<br />\n到底有無成功轉型既案例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55098e5325c7883f892b1e465daff20c1ec77c72","tid":119470,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未打完就post左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就打到呢到 有相似經驗嘅巴絲可以分享下<br />\n到底有無成功轉型既案例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿源？"},{"pid":"22014e602715534b6b936e946ba875845c37a9ec","tid":119470,"uid":5815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:40:33.000Z","msg":"呢啲兄弟姊妹預左跟你一世，我亦已經有咁既打算<br />\n我家姐除左廢之外，會食煙飲酒，以前仲吸過毒<br />\n響我眼中佢同一般垃圾無乜分別，但佢竟然係個資優生，所以連帶住有抑鬱症。<br />\n差人錢唔還，要老豆老母還<br />\n成廿幾歲人都仲問緊屋企人拎錢，終日響屋企打online game，佢衰左乜野都係賴個病，無一份工做得長過2個月。<br />\n但有時啲野話變就變，佢突然搵到佢既興趣，就會醒"},{"pid":"7ecaaf96d208bfeeecd62ab42fb26db52e3fd31a","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未打完就post左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就打到呢到 有相似經驗嘅巴絲可以分享下<br />\n到底有無成功轉型既案例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿源？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起碼阿源都會嘗試搵工脫毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebdd4ed72659ddb4a29900882f747ad5c05cf6d","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲兄弟姊妹預左跟你一世，我亦已經有咁既打算<br />\n我家姐除左廢之外，會食煙飲酒，以前仲吸過毒<br />\n響我眼中佢同一般垃圾無乜分別，但佢竟然係個資優生，所以連帶住有抑鬱症。<br />\n差人錢唔還，要老豆老母還<br />\n成廿幾歲人都仲問緊屋企人拎錢，終日響屋企打online game，佢衰左乜野都係賴個病，無一份工做得長過2個月。<br />\n但有時啲野話變就變，佢突然搵到佢既興趣，就會醒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁巴打家姐而家已經搵到興趣？<br />\n我都已經有遲早要自己擔起成頭家嘅心理準備...<br />\n共勉之呀巴打"},{"pid":"4eb36f2d18f35fb20142e34d060c33e7e6693655","tid":119470,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T19:04:44.000Z","msg":"焦慮症係屋企廢緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276fdcaf2b7bb1311d8e4dcd909315d5430c8a7d","tid":119470,"uid":1467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T19:07:46.000Z","msg":"幫佢搵女朋友"},{"pid":"efd651155b2842e66dab9c68af4ff52f5aab80a1","tid":119470,"uid":82960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T19:20:35.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢青中,會成日set目標比自己,但唔會做,話搵工話左幾個月都無搵.中意係屋企. 相反我妹好好動,好social,好多朋友,又番興趣班個啲(佢讀緊書) 不過好彩係佢無嫌棄我成日做廢青,又唔會話教訓我煩我,佢最多係笑下我毒,無乜朋友唔social咁"},{"pid":"7a4820cc9ef1a55ab077f316f73bc0a575ef6b77","tid":119470,"uid":41638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T19:48:54.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以比啲哲學書佢睇下"},{"pid":"68ecdfc61fe9d7aa808a24ff958cfc76bde16b41","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>焦慮症係屋企廢緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家有讀到相關嘅嘢<br />\n覺得巴打發現到甚至肯面對係好了不起"},{"pid":"51212acce52946fcac563466d602326bb58a8119","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫佢搵女朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪應該搵左個朋友再考慮咁親密嘅關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6fb8593f958749c53b0de785cae59f68c59971","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以講自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢青中,會成日set目標比自己,但唔會做,話搵工話左幾個月都無搵.中意係屋企. 相反我妹好好動,好social,好多朋友,又番興趣班個啲(佢讀緊書) 不過好彩係佢無嫌棄我成日做廢青,又唔會話教訓我煩我,佢最多係笑下我毒,無乜朋友唔social咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪我阿哥黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我好少攞黎笑佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed82464d3c721d98d2c2d88305a8eef702f06a9","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得可以比啲哲學書佢睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢本身睇好多哲學/歷史書<br />\n成日睇新聞個時講歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09699519c87b3cf82828fdf99c3dcfd0f45c05c6","tid":119470,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做人阿哥，但係成個死毒撚咁<br />\n從來冇人約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇朋友冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個星期日都r佢地出街一齊食飯（我請）<br />\n暫時好融洽愉快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地最鐘意串我幾年都唔買衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年仲請過佢地去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢地都開始拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我諗好快就剩低我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2615f75a39703d992f192472c225a56518bea1c1","tid":119470,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:38:04.000Z","msg":"我家姐個細佬係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢有返工 其他時間就係睇動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133759ec6b387250b502d9cd6e6d980d9061608a","tid":119470,"uid":42414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做人阿哥，但係成個死毒撚咁<br />\n從來冇人約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇朋友冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個星期日都r佢地出街一齊食飯（我請）<br />\n暫時好融洽愉快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地最鐘意串我幾年都唔買衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年仲請過佢地去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢地都開始拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我諗好快就剩低我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以請我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0913c20075a5e21ceffbc6e53e25018f6d0e6bd8","tid":119470,"uid":41638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得可以比啲哲學書佢睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢本身睇好多哲學/歷史書<br />\n成日睇新聞個時講歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我覺得又唔係廢青，係行為上比社會歸類做廢青"},{"pid":"867347d45f7b702471b1a978ca5327cdd2ca9136","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:18:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我家姐個細佬係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢有返工 其他時間就係睇動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動畫係興趣 我都成日煲漫畫動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5624cd7eb1030a5336a14a0102f49798b235d961","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做人阿哥，但係成個死毒撚咁<br />\n從來冇人約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇朋友冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個星期日都r佢地出街一齊食飯（我請）<br />\n暫時好融洽愉快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地最鐘意串我幾年都唔買衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年仲請過佢地去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢地都開始拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我諗好快就剩低我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nR你細佬/妹d朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n月入幾多先可以咁理財都生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac4541dd18d2d74b57561a90dd6c5cf78ef57b2","tid":119470,"uid":25225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得可以比啲哲學書佢睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢本身睇好多哲學/歷史書<br />\n成日睇新聞個時講歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我覺得又唔係廢青，係行為上比社會歸類做廢青</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得佢某d方面係好聰穎<br />\n但唔肯接受有時為左喜歡嘅事情 必須先經過難受嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nE.g. 為旅行儲錢/為玩清project<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c182828704f5b9ad861bb2b7601b0bbd81094f33","tid":119470,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>焦慮症係屋企廢緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家有讀到相關嘅嘢<br />\n覺得巴打發現到甚至肯面對係好了不起</blockquote><br />\n其實不停搵緊工"},{"pid":"f6d2631434a7022ae6895792612ecf9a468fbfba","tid":119470,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"咁你阿哥有無影響到你屋企？"},{"pid":"97f016a0a