=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有過情緒病都無佢咁癲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b31c8a5421d55c710b88063d0057f920d4f8b87","tid":119470,"uid":2032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T00:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有個妹，今年廿五歲，我大佢三年<br />\n會考成績好好，27分，但之後AL 失手，1C4D,<br />\n明明都算唔差，但佢之前Jupas 亂排<br />\n只可以入Poly product engineering ，呢科佢完全無興趣<br />\n之後佢就成個人頹廢哂<br />\n<br />\n咁到兩年前就普通成績Grad 之後就唔揾工<br />\n日日坐喺屋企hea<br />\n叫佢揾工又話自己揾緊，但就無着過suit<br />\n老豆老母又唔敢問佢，只係識擔心<br />\n<br />\n咁hea 左一年，我都認唔住當住老豆老母面前鬧足佢兩個鐘<br />\n咁先去揾份hea 工，喺啲工廠大厦做文員，得一萬蚊<br />\n咁樣就做左一年幾無諗過轉工<br />\n一放工就返屋企入房煲劇<br />\n<br />\n我老豆老母搭哂親戚朋友幫佢轉工<br />\n次次見完工，人地俾面兩老話請佢，佢又話其實唔想做，唔做<br />\n<br />\n我地屋企中等啦，無樓但都叫衣食不缺<br />\n我父母諗住俾錢佢去讀master<br />\n佢就好呀好呀，諗下讀乜<br />\n諗左兩年幾<br />\n<br />\n唉<br />\n宜家成廿五歲人，仲on99 <br />\n揾人埋單都難<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉<br />\n明明佢讀書唔差，起碼大學生<br />\n英文聽落勁(CE 英文 straight A)<br />\n點解佢唔揾份好啲嘅工，起碼之後有機會升都好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有過情緒病都無佢咁癲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉<br />\n我地都覺得佢有病，需要你開解下治癒下<br />\n但點開口？佢覺得自己無問題，唔需要幫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9637769d7a1f903539b8c06d9089177451a3ce08","tid":119470,"uid":13271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T01:35:29.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n我曾經雙失過三年半。<br />\n果陣每日都係上高登打J睇動畫玩galgame同打機，冇讀書冇做野。<br />\n因為行錯左步搞到做雙失，所以好後悔諗野好灰暗同冇自信<br />\n其實佢好需要人關心一下，冇朋友更加要關心佢<br />\n我依家做左野一年，鍾意左個女仔，決心要脫毒改變自己，冇再打過機"},{"pid":"6a6e9ef716590b90c02fc90e0df0778a3678eaa0","tid":119470,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好理佢啦"},{"pid":"653828051f5f6831da1e02459b5a7af64c604fb9","tid":119470,"uid":63290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我家姐個細佬係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢有返工 其他時間就係睇動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你家姐個細佬，咪姐係你囉"},{"pid":"bf9a7e00a6555fb71a4245c982a4b940ddb707d6","tid":119470,"uid":63290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做人阿哥，但係成個死毒撚咁<br />\n從來冇人約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇朋友冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個星期日都r佢地出街一齊食飯（我請）<br />\n暫時好融洽愉快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地最鐘意串我幾年都唔買衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年仲請過佢地去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢地都開始拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我諗好快就剩低我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nR你細佬/妹d朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n月入幾多先可以咁理財都生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請細佬妹姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n月入2萬尾<br />\n單身未拍過拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，冇養車跟屋企住<br />\n冇追科技野，iPhone隔代換<br />\n永遠著同一套衫出街<br />\n放工直接返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本上唔去旅行係洗唔到錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n月入係你嘅一半，租緊人地個廳訓，廢青一個。"},{"pid":"5e3bb1dd56bffae7dd80bc0ed61c601523bebb24","tid":119470,"uid":52760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:22:15.000Z","msg":"26歲廢青here<br />\n利申：讀緊醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1e1df23a5c5f977d56c52d28af7c6c68ee3d9d","tid":119470,"uid":13335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"我男友個細佬已經係屋企毒左兩年<br />\n日日訓醒就起身打機玩電話<br />\n食完就訓唔知幾耐冇出過街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d73040b53c39726aa25d8bc8827a4d6d4b3638","tid":119470,"uid":6644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:24:42.000Z","msg":"呢個情況只有三樣野幫到佢<br />\n<br />\n1.信仰<br />\n2.女友<br />\n3.死亡<br />\n<br />\n意見只供參考"},{"pid":"a994341e7f0ad968f5c5eef7a258126b8bf7e5d1","tid":119470,"uid":1997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:24:48.000Z","msg":"有 不過係我 我細佬死mk仔成日帶女上屋企<br />\n有次仲比左條女個波我渣 我諗係我人生唯一一次有異性接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e4ec9eff0b22d0c49b2d1654be8d37e69b973e","tid":119470,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"雙失的話絕對絕對唔好打機<br />\n但坐電腦面前一日都可以<br />\n<br />\n過來人，試過一次要花半年搵工<br />\n份工做到而家都成十幾年"},{"pid":"81b4b03c7918840fa1476505e1b51fdcb7945871","tid":119470,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有個妹，今年廿五歲，我大佢三年<br />\n會考成績好好，27分，但之後AL 失手，1C4D,<br />\n明明都算唔差，但佢之前Jupas 亂排<br />\n只可以入Poly product engineering ，呢科佢完全無興趣<br />\n之後佢就成個人頹廢哂<br />\n<br />\n咁到兩年前就普通成績Grad 之後就唔揾工<br />\n日日坐喺屋企hea<br />\n叫佢揾工又話自己揾緊，但就無着過suit<br />\n老豆老母又唔敢問佢，只係識擔心<br />\n<br />\n咁hea 左一年，我都認唔住當住老豆老母面前鬧足佢兩個鐘<br />\n咁先去揾份hea 工，喺啲工廠大厦做文員，得一萬蚊<br />\n咁樣就做左一年幾無諗過轉工<br />\n一放工就返屋企入房煲劇<br />\n<br />\n我老豆老母搭哂親戚朋友幫佢轉工<br />\n次次見完工，人地俾面兩老話請佢，佢又話其實唔想做，唔做<br />\n<br />\n我地屋企中等啦，無樓但都叫衣食不缺<br />\n我父母諗住俾錢佢去讀master<br />\n佢就好呀好呀，諗下讀乜<br />\n諗左兩年幾<br />\n<br />\n唉<br />\n宜家成廿五歲人，仲on99 <br />\n揾人埋單都難<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我朋友讀呢科grad 而家十皮一個月"},{"pid":"c3ad877a5e3754f4cb8943e4f2ef7d0a805d10bc","tid":119470,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個情況只有三樣野幫到佢<br />\n<br />\n1.信仰<br />\n2.女友<br />\n3.死亡<br />\n<br />\n意見只供參考</blockquote><br />\n果時我係老母鞭策"},{"pid":"a1029abedb684bdd5716de9cfffcc50349dd5895","tid":119470,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 不過係我 我細佬死mk仔成日帶女上屋企<br />\n有次仲比左條女個波我渣 我諗係我人生唯一一次有異性接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1f6b41210bad3103d177433e571fc03bfce318","tid":119470,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有 不過係我 我細佬死mk仔成日帶女上屋企<br />\n有次仲比左條女個波我渣 我諗係我人生唯一一次有異性接觸<img src=\"/as