=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n四海之內皆_兄弟...<br />\n先由屋企做起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8e765e64bc984d1cff81b8530181fc8382f234","tid":119470,"uid":50819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有個妹，今年廿五歲，我大佢三年<br />\n會考成績好好，27分，但之後AL 失手，1C4D,<br />\n明明都算唔差，但佢之前Jupas 亂排<br />\n只可以入Poly product engineering ，呢科佢完全無興趣<br />\n之後佢就成個人頹廢哂<br />\n<br />\n咁到兩年前就普通成績Grad 之後就唔揾工<br />\n日日坐喺屋企hea<br />\n叫佢揾工又話自己揾緊，但就無着過suit<br />\n老豆老母又唔敢問佢，只係識擔心<br />\n<br />\n咁hea 左一年，我都認唔住當住老豆老母面前鬧足佢兩個鐘<br />\n咁先去揾份hea 工，喺啲工廠大厦做文員，得一萬蚊<br />\n咁樣就做左一年幾無諗過轉工<br />\n一放工就返屋企入房煲劇<br />\n<br />\n我老豆老母搭哂親戚朋友幫佢轉工<br />\n次次見完工，人地俾面兩老話請佢，佢又話其實唔想做，唔做<br />\n<br />\n我地屋企中等啦，無樓但都叫衣食不缺<br />\n我父母諗住俾錢佢去讀master<br />\n佢就好呀好呀，諗下讀乜<br />\n諗左兩年幾<br />\n<br />\n唉<br />\n宜家成廿五歲人，仲on99 <br />\n揾人埋單都難<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我朋友讀呢科grad 而家十皮一個月</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都覺唔關讀乜科事<br />\n你夠醒夠勤力一定唔會差得去邊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會考27分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係由高考失手一直頹? 讀大學時有冇咩大事發生過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26590cb022f2e2100060fb822d0becb1aeaceec9","tid":119470,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:44:55.000Z","msg":"我家姐有個廢青細佬<br />\n啫係我"},{"pid":"549f5f689b34f4efe59e054eaecdf11031894c56","tid":119470,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:46:44.000Z","msg":"其實廢青心裡面都有夢想<br />\n只係覺得做唔到，諗野負面，放棄狀態<br />\n俾d自信，鼓勵就ok<br />\n最緊要令佢知佢自己都做到"},{"pid":"6a2c405331d7a98885173447730c5313dcc82f0a","tid":119470,"uid":40682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:47:52.000Z","msg":"老豆個阿哥<br />\n唔知點解冇做嘢冇結婚"},{"pid":"941342745520db6aadd455cd81aad4b8b0fcf51f","tid":119470,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我家姐個細佬係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢有返工 其他時間就係睇動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你家姐個細佬，咪姐係你囉</blockquote><br />\n叻叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9be0d0d4b9926d6d94d896cbf030e6dbe233506","tid":119470,"uid":40682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆個阿哥<br />\n唔知點解冇做嘢冇結婚<br />\n依家又癡肥又周身病咬緊遺產<br />\n一年入幾次醫院<br />\n我老豆仲要俾錢養佢照顧佢<br />\n仲同佢請工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"fb8841fde154725b6fdbf9c4fefb48b4ff1b8548","tid":119470,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:55:16.000Z","msg":"嚇死我 以為講緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf250511908a69d869c1ba8284a3af0c6a21051","tid":119470,"uid":34642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n資優 有抑鬱<br />\n小學同中學成績好好 但係越大越頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學開始越黎越毒 宜家已經進化成完全體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀緊大學 冇朋友<br />\n好少返學 淨係返去考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日係屋企睇動漫 打機 天光先瞓 <br />\n冇目標 冇動力 唔想返工 畢業應該會變廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩屋企人好好 冇嫌過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時頂唔順先會話